# nghttp2 reachable assertion / DoS — fixed in nghttp2 v1.68.1.
# Suppressed because Alpine has not yet packaged the fix; the Dockerfile
# already runs `apk upgrade --no-cache` so this will clear automatically
# once the Alpine repo ships nghttp2 >=1.68.1.
CVE-2026-27135

# OpenSSL Heap Use-After-Free in PKCS7_verify() — fixed in libcrypto3/libssl3 3.5.7-r0.
# Suppressed because Alpine has not yet packaged the fix; the Dockerfile
# already runs `apk upgrade --no-cache` and explicitly installs libcrypto3/libssl3
# so this will clear automatically once Alpine ships >=3.5.7-r0.
CVE-2026-45447
